# Find the Quartiles of GDP per Capita

min_gpc = min(df['GDP_per_Capita'])
q25 = df['GDP_per_Capita'].quantile(.25)
q50 = df['GDP_per_Capita'].quantile(.50)
q75 = df['GDP_per_Capita'].quantile(.75)
max_gpc = max(df['GDP_per_Capita'])
print("GDP per Capita")
print(f"min={min_gpc}, q25={q25}, q50={q50}, q75={q75}, max={max_gpc}")

# Group countries into quartiles

group3 = df[(df['GDP_per_Capita'] > q50) & (df['GDP_per_Capita'] <= q75)].sort_values(by='GDP_per_Capita', ascending=False).copy()
